# Netflix EDA Analysis

This repository contains an exploratory data analysis (EDA) project on the Netflix dataset.

The analysis includes:

* Data cleaning and preprocessing
* Exploratory data analysis using visualizations
* Key business insights derived from the data

The complete notebook for this project is developed using Google Colab and will be linked here.

## Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib / Seaborn
* Google Colab

